Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:09.01,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}I had lost my way during my journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:17.02,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Only my soul was wandering, while I stood still.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:25.28,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}But right now, I'm walking to a distant place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:33.53,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}That's right, ever since I met you on this road.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:41.96,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}The travellers witnessed the song, the forbidden song,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:52.72,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}And I became attached to it as I heard it alone with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:01:00.81,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}If the world I saw in my dreams exists somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:09.20,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Let's go search for it, beyond the winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:13.37,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Whether it's a freezing dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:17.58,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A dry midday,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:21.75,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A shivering night,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.75,0:01:28.00,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}or the ends of the Earth, let's go and see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:06.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How many did you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.90,0:02:09.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Seventeen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.18,0:02:10.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, eighteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:13.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, maybe nineteen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:14.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And how much is left?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:17.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:18.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just for reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:20.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You already know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:21.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just in case, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:23.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Eighty...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:24.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Eighty what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.59,0:02:25.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Eighty-one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:32.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I just have to eat them, right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:33.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you even able to eat them all?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:35.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.02,0:02:37.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Horo the Wise from Yoitsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:39.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to be so obstinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:41.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.48,0:02:42.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:43.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:45.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the real truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:47.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the real truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:49.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the real, real, real truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:52.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the real, real, real truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:55.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I'm already tired of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:02:58.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:03.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they're your favorite food, you had twenty yesterday and almost as many today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:05.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:08.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll show you I can eat them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:15.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't get so worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:19.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be tired of fresh apples, but there are several ways to eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:24.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And what exactly are these "severals ways to eat them?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:31.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't ridicule me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:34.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of apples being baked before!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:38.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You've seriously never eaten apple pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:41.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a thing really exists?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.19,0:03:44.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you bake it in a pan with dough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:47.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you do that, it becomes chewy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:51.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a good way of explaining it, but it's like it's slowly rotting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:57.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But just like how something about to rot is good, baked apples are very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.97,0:04:01.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,When you eat fresh apples, they moisten your dry throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:03.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But baked apples are so sweet that they make your throat dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:09.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure you're tired of sweet food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:13.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we'll have a change of pace for dinner and have salted meat or fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:14.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Which would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:15.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:19.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And who was it just now who looked like they couldn't eat any more?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:22.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a different story if it's meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:24.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:28.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really counting on you with the apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:29.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:33.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I have confidence I can eat them all after hearing your story!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:36.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have some business too, so let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:37.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:48.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I changed the mood so that you wouldn't get tired of {\i1}me{\i0}, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:52.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're inedible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:55.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you want me to say that I'm delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.59,0:04:56.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:05:01.50,Chapter Name Title Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Wolf and Blessed Tail
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:08.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:11.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:14.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I say it? You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:28.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You really do look like a nun, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:31.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, it's convenient for traveling, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:32.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:36.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,People are as strange as ever, being so particular
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:38.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,about whether to wear all these different clothes or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:44.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There are times when it's convenient for \Nwolves to wear sheep's clothing too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:46.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:50.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If I wore rabbit's fur, I'm sure you'd fall into my trap instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:55.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll carry around some \Napples so that I'll get caught in a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.51,0:05:58.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I even forgot about apples as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:02.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And so!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:07.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In your case, you look too much like a nun, so there are times when it'd be inconvenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.94,0:06:08.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Like when?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:12.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much a nun may have fallen, they wouldn't drink beer in the middle of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:15.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quite the nun, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:18.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A nun wouldn't say that either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:21.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:27.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously though, there will be places where dressing as a nun would be a bad idea once we head north.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:31.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:32.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:37.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it'd be a safe idea for you to have a set of clothes like a city girl's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:45.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go and buy some before we eat, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:49.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're held back by business, our meal won't be as good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:52.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you, I didn't have to waste time explaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:56.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you thinking I'd say we should eat and drink first?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.11,0:06:58.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't get distracted by food that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:06:59.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:04.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I was being considerate for you, and you bought it so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:09.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You came up with such an exaggerated reason just to buy a set of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:12.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think I wouldn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:16.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll hold back and let you buy me some clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:18.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be a cold, cold winter, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:20.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You can hold back a little more, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:25.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:26.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:29.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:32.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying I don't have small change.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Better too big than too small, as they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:39.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So you just need to use that money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:42.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's also the saying about cutting a rabbit with a meat cleaver.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:46.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If I used this money at a clothes store, \NI can't imagine how displeased they'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:51.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But are gold coins really worth so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:52.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:58.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, the current Rumione gold coin is worth thirty-five Thoreni silver coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:08:01.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you live humbly, one silver coin can last you seven days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:04.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's worth thirty-five times that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:06.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:07.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:10.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The store said that these clothes are worth two gold coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:15.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike apples, wouldn't clothes be \Nsomething you'd buy with gold coins?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:19.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If that were true, most of the people in the city would be naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:24.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the merchant who sold those clothes \Nmust've been quite worried about if you'd even pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:27.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Were these that expensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:28.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:31.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So choose some shabby-looking clothes when we buy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:34.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Horo the Wise from Yoitsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.93,0:08:38.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If I wear something shabby, it'll hurt my pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:41.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that if you are truly beautiful, then anything should look good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:45.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, to the money exchange, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:46.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we're going to exchange money?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we're going to that bridge, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:52.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:56.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to drink some beer soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:02.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumione, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:06.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's market price for it is thirty-four Thoreni silver coins on the dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:08.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And the handling charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:13.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten Liuto coins, or thirty Trie coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:15.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay in Liuto coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:19.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:21.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:25.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you drop them, they'll belong to whoever picks it up off the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:28.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Weiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:30.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:32.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm{\i0} the customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:36.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the gold coin there, I'm busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:40.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you're not even treating your precious customers properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:46.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more important that this precious little lady doesn't drop any coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:47.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:49.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,My, that makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:51.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But, dear sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:52.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:56.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There are just too many coins for my hand to hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:10:01.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why my hand is there, Horo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:04.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,My, but we can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:07.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to use your precious hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:12.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all, I will gladly use my hands so that these coins won't fall from your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:15.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It does not trouble me in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:20.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That is because you are like a warm feeling in my chest that cannot be held with both arms,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:24.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and there's no doubt that you'll accept it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:25.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Weiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:28.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget the basics of being a money exchanger?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:30.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Silver in a bag, gold in a chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:32.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be holding on to crude copper coins in your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:34.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:38.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Keeping such a good girl to yourself is an act against God.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.37,0:10:41.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you heard the passage that says to share what bread you can offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:43.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to share?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:47.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't share with you on top of the money exchanging fee, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:49.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I either give you everything or nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:54.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, then she'll come with the debt she owes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:10:57.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I believe that you need to show some level of determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:03.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't possibly place a price on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:06.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how can you say that, you corrupt merchant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:12.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The scale in my heart is tilting back and forth right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:17.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But please, believe that it is not tilting because of the weight of gold coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:20.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Of course I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.10,0:11:26.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a bad person, to touch a tilting scale with your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:28.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.26,0:11:32.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:34.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:39.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to exchange some gold coins, so are you going shopping or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:40.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:43.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Prices seem like they're going to rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:44.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Since that's the case, the faster, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.25,0:11:47.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:51.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do money exchangers even work when the sun sets?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:57.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's a rule that money exchangers who use scales after the sun sets are swindlers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:12:00.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, I'm no swindler.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:02.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:04.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I buy clothes, I'll be going to the tavern early.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:07.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You can come if you want when you're done working.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:08.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.84,0:12:10.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the usual tavern, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:13.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's scary to be drunk at a tavern I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:16.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:19.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be soon! I'll really be there soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:28.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It was as interesting as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:30.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be troublesome later if you get him too serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:32.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Troublesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:33.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll follow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:35.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:39.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I played around knowing that, unlike you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:42.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun teasing you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:44.45,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,but I want to play with some smart males sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:50.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You both knew I was playing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.14,0:12:52.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So could you not act so serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:55.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start blushing instead, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:13:00.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that Weiz fellow is more of an eloquent talker than you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:03.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lived for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:06.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,but I've never met anyone like him, whose words I cannot trust at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:11.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you, who lives in the business world, would understand this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:16.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. If it were beneficial for me, I'd lie as much as needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:18.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't work on me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go shopping for clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.71,0:13:24.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:29.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You've missed your chance two times to grasp the blessing God granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:35.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't grasp it next time, the tail of blessing might run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:37.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:39.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Horo! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:54.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That one right there is forty Liuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:56.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite durable for that price.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:04.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading north, so could you find something that's cheap and warm for the two us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:07.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your budget?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:09.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Two Thoreni coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:11.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:15.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A set of robes, two blankets...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.07,0:14:16.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And would something like this be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:20.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:22.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you can see, I'm a merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:26.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,On my travels, I became friends with the Milone Company here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:28.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? With Mr. Milone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:33.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, so that's why I may come \Nseveral times a year from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:35.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:40.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me add another blanket along with this robe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:43.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, they've been smoked,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:45.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,so I guarantee that they'll repel bugs for two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:01.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't we come to buy clothes for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.95,0:15:02.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:06.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me to wear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.08,0:15:10.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can get away from the cold with just that robe, then it should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.23,0:15:16.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're angry because I used your enemy, then say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:18.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Horo the Wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:21.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm smart and I have a good business sense, but my nose is sharp too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:24.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The day I wear that, my nose will turn up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:28.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought having you suffer a bit might fix that twisted personality of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:32.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you in on the secret later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:37.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:38.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:41.45,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any nice clothes for women?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:43.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Clothes for women?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:45.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that won't cause much trouble in northern cities,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:47.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,something about her size.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:55.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:57.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:01.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a court attendant's dress that was bought from a certain store, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:04.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want something that gaudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:07.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't suit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:10.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I want something simpler and easy to change into.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:14.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:18.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, how about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:19.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.90,0:16:22.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:26.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite the person, to have laid your eyes on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:30.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,These articles were once worn by a certain noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.73,0:16:35.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look, the seams are sewn neatly, and it won't tear so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:38.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What you should really be looking at is this walnut-colored cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.34,0:16:40.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you wear this over your shoulder,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.49,0:16:46.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and wear this specially tailored triangular cap just like the servants at this noble's house,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:50.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll become a city girl immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:53.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A rabbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:55.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it make you want to eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:56.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.55,0:16:58.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How much is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:00.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,For the two of them, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:02.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten Thoreni coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:04.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, how about nine coins?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:07.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:11.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In deference to the beautiful lady here, I'll make it eight coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:14.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:20.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How about someone cute, such as myself, were to wear these to open your heart? Would you make it seven coins?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:28.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,V-Very well, I'll let you have it for seven coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:29.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.97,0:17:32.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:44.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:49.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,One Thoreni coin is not even enough for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:56.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Were these clothes too expensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:59.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, seven coins for those is quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:03.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You still had enough confidence to drive the price down?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.99,0:18:07.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had gotten similar clothes like the ones you're carrying over your shoulder,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:10.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would have been okay for being a tenth of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.76,0:18:11.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:14.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually thought it would've cost more, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:15.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:18.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you hold back on drinking later,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:21.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll make up for the seven coins right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:23.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't drink that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:30.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, the way you forcefully \Nbargained with him was really cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:34.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how great a merchant may be, they wouldn't be able to stand up to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:37.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,All males are idiots, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:41.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it with you to the tavern?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:45.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:48.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But the inn isn't this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:50.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I won't be leaving it at the inn either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:54.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to sell these at a different clothes shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:58.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We can buy some clothes for the cold when we head a bit more north.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:01.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to sell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:04.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in keeping them if we're not going to use them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:09.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, but will they sell high?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:10.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:13.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaining a profit would be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:14.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll probably have a bit of a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:17.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still going to sell them if you have a loss?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.89,0:19:19.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:21.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, I'm thinking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:31.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I tell you the secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:34.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ask you to tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:36.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you want to say it, then go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:42.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it's nothing great, and you were more amazing back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.89,0:19:46.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This bunch of clothes is worth two coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:50.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, let's say we sell these at a different store for half the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.03,0:19:51.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have a loss of one coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:53.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:56.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But, let's think of it a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:19:58.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A different way?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:20:03.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, everyone would think that the robe you're wearing is high-grade, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:04.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Robe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:08.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's safe to say that a person wearing that wouldn't ever go to a shop like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:14.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why that shop keeper actually wanted to have a good relation with me, who brought you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:17.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, if it were you, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:20.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd sell things cheap to leave a good impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:21.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.91,0:20:23.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And what would lead from that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:28.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That store lost a bit off these.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:30.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And they lost {\i1}quite {\i0}a bit off yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:36.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We bought these near-ragged clothes for two coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:40.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there is a huge gap between the two prices.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.43,0:20:42.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And what would lead from that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.02,0:20:46.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If we think about the difference, there is a huge profit gained.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:48.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:54.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cheap trick. A completely cheap trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:20:57.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.35,0:20:58.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:01.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed you even thought of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:03.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's called business sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.31,0:21:08.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But yours beat mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:13.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Your shallow thinking can't beat my planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:14.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You said it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:16.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can win?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:18.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you're confident about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.87,0:21:22.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe you could show me your skills when we go drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:23.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,When we go drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:28.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you buy me at a high price?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.39,0:21:29.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'll buy you.
